extendedInfo.description: Run, Run, Run! Forest Runner is a fast paced jumping game.Tap screen or trackball to jump to avoid obstacles in your forest adventure! Simple game rule but it's surprisingly challenging. Enjoy to be a Forest Runner!

reviews.comment: After you finish the eight levels, there aren\'t any more levels. and the bad .part is that you can\'t even do anything else when your done except uninstall it. Booooo forest runner boooo!!!! But other than that the game is average.
